      "text": "(upbeat music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 2790.0,
      "end_time": 3541.0,
      "text": "[Narrator] Just over 30 miles away"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 3541.0,
      "end_time": 5768.0,
      "text": "from the Slovenian capital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 5768.0,
      "end_time": 7819.0,
      "text": "this alpine lake looks like it belongs"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 7819.0,
      "end_time": 10152.0,
      "text": "on the cover of a storybook."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 17216.0,
      "end_time": 19390.0,
      "text": "With a fairytale cliff-side castle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 19390.0,
      "end_time": 21502.0,
      "text": "an emerald green freshwater lake,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 21502.0,
      "end_time": 25510.0,
      "text": "and views of some of the highest peaks of the Julian Alps,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 25510.0,
      "end_time": 26980.0,
      "text": "Lake Bled and its island church"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 26981.0,
      "end_time": 29481.0,
      "text": "make a postcard-perfect scene."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 30773.0,
      "end_time": 32719.0,
      "text": "To visit the Assumption of Mary Church,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 32719.0,
      "end_time": 36502.0,
      "text": "you must catch a ride on a wooden boat known as a plenta."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 36502.0,
      "end_time": 38263.0,
      "text": "Plentas have been taking visitors to the island"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 38263.0,
      "end_time": 41596.0,
      "text": "in the middle of the lake for centuries."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 43231.0,
      "end_time": 46409.0,
      "text": "Once reaching the island, it's a 99-stone-step climb"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 46409.0,
      "end_time": 49184.0,
      "text": "to reach the entrance to the church."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 49184.0,
      "end_time": 51260.0,
      "text": "It is said that if a groom could carry his bride"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 51260.0,
      "end_time": 54940.0,
      "text": "up these steps and ring the wishing bell at the top,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 54940.0,
      "end_time": 57772.0,
      "text": "the marriage would be a happy one."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 59659.0,
      "end_time": 61416.0,
      "text": "The church is most famous for this bell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 61416.0,
      "end_time": 64137.0,
      "text": "which was made in the early 16th century"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 64138.00000000001,
      "end_time": 68560.0,
      "text": "and is said to be a gift from the Pope."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 68560.0,
      "end_time": 70914.0,
      "text": "Legend has it this was the church's second bell."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 70915.0,
      "end_time": 73946.0,
      "text": "The first was bought for the church by an inconsolable widow"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 73946.0,
      "end_time": 75521.0,
      "text": "in honor of her late husband"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 75522.0,
      "end_time": 79610.0,
      "text": "who was murdered and then thrown into the lake."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 79610.0,
      "end_time": 80972.0,
      "text": "When boatmen brought it across to the church,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 80972.0,
      "end_time": 82684.0,
      "text": "an unexpected storm hit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 82684.0,
      "end_time": 85351.0,
      "text": "and the bell sunk to the bottom."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 88187.0,
      "end_time": 90987.0,
      "text": "It is said if you listen closely in the dead of night,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 90987.0,
      "end_time": 92170.0,
      "text": "you can hear the sunken bell"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 92170.0,
      "end_time": 95179.0,
      "text": "ringing from the depths of this picturesque lake."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 95179.0,
      "end_time": 97762.0,
      "text": "(upbeat music)"
    }
  ]
}